Text:
The keygen will NOT work... unless you do the following (really I'm not sure why you didn't include this in your instructions...)

Open the Keygen

Click on the '+' button on the right of the 'Reset' button.

A'Debug' interface will slide up.

Enter 'b934' (without quotes) into the 'year' slot.

Click the 'Generate' button.

This will trick the keygen to generate a code for 2011.
